# HKDevicePlacementSide.left

**Case**

A device predominately located on the left side.

## Declaration

```swift
case left
```

## Placements

- **HKDevicePlacementSide.central**: A device predominately located near the center of the body.
- **HKDevicePlacementSide.right**: A device predominately located on the right side.
- **HKDevicePlacementSide.unknown**: The system couldn’t determine the device’s placement.
